    "causal_summary": "This is **Phase 2** of the Reorganize sk-doc/assets reorganization. After Phase 1 physically moved 4 asset items to `assets/` root and deleted the empty `agents/` subfolder, all dependent references still point to the OLD paths. Phase 2 closes that gap by applying 4 fixed-string substring substitutions across the canonical `.opencode/` tree and then replicating the changes to the other 3 runtime mirrors (`.claude/`, `.codex/`, `.gemini/`).",
